		<div class="featured-image-wrapper" data-interchange="[http://i0.wp.com/fusiondotnet.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fusion_blackberry_-croopped.jpg?resize=640%2C269.91304347826&amp;quality=80&amp;strip=all, (small)],[http://i0.wp.com/fusiondotnet.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fusion_blackberry_-croopped.jpg?resize=1280%2C539.82608695652&amp;quality=80&amp;strip=all, (smallretina)],[http://i0.wp.com/fusiondotnet.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fusion_blackberry_-croopped.jpg?resize=1024%2C431.86086956522&amp;quality=80&amp;strip=all, (medium)],[http://i0.wp.com/fusiondotnet.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fusion_blackberry_-croopped.jpg?resize=1380%2C582&amp;quality=80&amp;strip=all, (mediumretina)],[http://i0.wp.com/fusiondotnet.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fusion_blackberry_-croopped.jpg?resize=1380%2C582&amp;quality=80&amp;strip=all, (large)],[http://i0.wp.com/fusiondotnet.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/fusion_blackberry_-croopped.jpg?resize=1380%2C582&amp;quality=80&amp;strip=all, (largeretina)]">
