			<div class="kicker">The Battle of Waterloo</div>
	
	<h1 id="single-title" class="main-title">The life, death, and rebirth of BlackBerry&#8217;s hometown</h1>

	
	<div>
		<span class="byline">by <a href="http://fusion.net/author/kevin-roose/">Kevin Roose</a></span> <span class="date">| February 8, 2015</span>
	</div>
</div>
			</div>

